  <name>FolderZipper Versioning</name>
  <summary>Folder compression with automatic versioning</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      FolderZipperVersioning is a smart backup utility for compressing folders with automatic version control.
      It features an intuitive GUI, custom version input, auto-increment versioning, and timestamps in filenames.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Easy folder selection via built-in browser</li>
      <li>Automatic version numbering (001, 002, 003...)</li>
      <li>Custom version input field (e.g., 1.0.1)</li>
      <li>Timestamp in zip filenames</li>
      <li>Dark mode support for Windows</li>
      <li>Directory navigation</li>
      <li>Real-time status feedback</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
